natTextualConventions.description: This MIB module defines the NATProtocolType textual convention for use in MIBs that need to identify the protocols which support network address translation.

NATProtocolType.name: NATProtocolType
NATProtocolType.description: A list of protocols that are affected/support network address translation. Inclusion of values is not intended to imply that those protocols need be supported.
